    "speaker": "interviewee",
    "tag": "AB",
    "text": "The picture was taken in the town of Lubeck, Germany. This is photograph of our present family taken in 1994 or '93, on a occasion where we were honored by Jewish Family and Children's Service, both Claire and I. Starting from the left is my son, Jonathan; then my daughter, Sari; my glorious, beautiful wife, Claire; and I.",
